text: Kaarle Tapper (born 19 September 1995) is a Finnish competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's Laser class. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Finland Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser Category:Sailors at the 2010 Summer Youth Olympics
